{"tid":1578130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"現實係個社會已經唔係一切正常,點解咁多風向叫人唔好搞馬場?","createTime":"2019-09-18T04:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T05:38:22.000Z","uid":88610,"like":11,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c14f56ff8e81e9a2200337b5350ba6d7cf9cc449","tid":1578130,"uid":88610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:38:50.000Z","msg":"可唔可以醒一醒 搞尻馬場同五大訴求有咩直接關係<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577905</a><br />\n呢D POST都會有成800個正評, 連登既質素真係每況愈下<br />\n頭場有何妖既馬, 如果有幾百人搞馬場就可以令一個所謂慈善機構跑唔成馬我覺得係好低成本就可以獲得好大成效既事<br />\n咁既社會風氣之下仲可以馬照跑舞照跳本來就已經係一件好荒謬既事<br />\n道理同罷工, 搞狗二代, 搞狗擺酒一樣, 唔係直接都絕對係間接比壓力政府同狗隊<br />\n馬場見"},{"pid":"4ba8a4545ff33002030b9c867ab6d6a1f89105f6","tid":1578130,"uid":88610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"6ae5286f853da2dfe155aca35ac62b833679b81e","tid":1578130,"uid":88610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"驅逐共黨"},{"pid":"61d581685baf3accd7f98f7ddaa0b13635411ec8","tid":1578130,"uid":88610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"馬場見"},{"pid":"f0b7f473bf1fd9fd23c224155688eb6e962a1c1d","tid":1578130,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht